TestCase #1
Summery: Check the authorization form
Pre-condition:
1.The user is registered on the site

Steps fo reproduce:
1. Enter valid login
2. Enter valid password
3. Click "Sing in" button

Expected result:
1. Displayed "Sing Out" button
-----------------------------------------------
TestCase #2
Summery:Check the creation of a "All Users" post
Pre-condition:
1.The user is authorization on the site

Steps fo reproduce:
1. Click "Create Post" button
2. Enter Title: "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit."
3. Enter Body Content: Nullam iaculis magna ac ex lobortis, quis porttitor urna fringilla.
                       Aliquam odio leo, fermentum sed magna euismod, fringilla semper ipsum.
                       Proin lacus nunc, venenatis volutpat orci ac, maximus sollicitudin ex.
                       Aliquam sit amet nibh eget ex euismod lacinia. Vestibulum semper quam
                       dui, mattis elementum ipsum hendrerit sit amet. Aenean vel ornare massa.
                        Curabitur metus nibh, bibendum non nisl sed, maximus ultrices arcu.
                        Nunc ut erat ultricies, iaculis mi nec, hendrerit nulla. Etiam eros
                        nisl, elementum et eros in, pharetra laoreet odio. Fusce a sollicitudin
                        nunc, sit amet finibus nisl. In hac habitasse platea dictumst.
                        Cras ullamcorper molestie massa, eget consectetur dolor elementum eu.
                         Sed dapibus auctor lectus eu facilisis.
4. Select value "All Users"
5. Click "Save New Post" button

Expected result:
1. Alert "New post successfully created." displayed
2. Note: This post was written for "All Users" displayed
-------------------------------------------------
